v1.1.2 Phase 72 (2026.7.12, same-version revision):
  - Version remains versionCode=112, versionName="1.1.2".
  - Bug fix: _reviewAnalyzeAdvance (ui.js, GPL v3) — "false completion"
    after long-press priority eval. The completion check now scans the
    ENTIRE range [0.._lastStep] for uncached steps.
  - AndroidManifest.xml: No changes.
  - License classification: unchanged — no new third-party code introduced.

v1.1.2 Phase 71 (2026.7.11, same-version revision):
  - Version remains versionCode=112, versionName="1.1.2".
  - Bug fix (user-reported): stats.html (GPL v3) CSP blocked inline onclick
    handlers → move selection broken. Fix: script-src switched from
    'sha256-<hash>' to 'unsafe-inline'. XSS hardening: movetext/variation/
    firstMoves now escaped via _escFEN. Chess960 0-distance castling fix
    across stats.html + ai-bridge.js + ui.js + game-logic.js.
  - Concurrency fixes: StockfishNative.java (GPL v3) readyOkLatchHolder race
    + engineStop TOCTOU + importSettings cap bypass.
  - StatsActivity.java (GPL v3): shouldOverrideUrlLoading deprecated overload
    + onRenderProcessGone.
  - Low-risk robustness patches: secureRandomInt/moveAlg/en-passant inB
    (game-logic.js, GPL v3); toShredderCastling board guard (chess960.js,
    AGPL v3); sevenTagRoster/composePGN null guards (pgn-standard.js, GPL v3);
    worker-pool.js 3-strike counter (GPL v3).
  - AndroidManifest.xml: No changes.
  - License classification: unchanged — no new third-party code introduced.

v1.1.2 Phase 70 (2026.7.10, same-version revision):
  - Version remains versionCode=112, versionName="1.1.2".
  - Bug fix: _pgnCacheBuildSaveContext (ui.js, GPL v3) — force-rebuild now
    checks _reviewEvalCache.size > 0 directly (not _inReview), so evals from
    a previous review session are included even after exiting review mode.
  - Robustness: makeMvInPlace (game-logic.js, GPL v3) — added inB() bounds
    check on to-coordinates (same fix as makeMv in Phase 67).
  - Redundancy cleanup: removed 7 debug console.log from ai-bridge.js (GPL v3)
    + 1 from eco-data.js (AGPL v3).
  - License classification: unchanged — no new third-party code introduced.

v1.1.2 Phase 69 (2026.7.9, same-version revision):
  - Version remains versionCode=112, versionName="1.1.2".
  - Bug 1+2: _pgnCacheSaveCurrentImpl (ui.js, GPL v3) — decoupled coverage check
    from _useOriginal; when _reviewEvalCache.size>0, force rebuild path so
    [%eval] annotations are included. Refactored into _pgnCacheBuildSaveContext
    + _pgnCacheBuildPGNText + _pgnCachePersistSave shared helpers.
  - Bug 3: _pgnCacheOpInProgress guard (ui.js, GPL v3) on all PGN cache operations.
  - Bug 4: build-chess.py (AGPL v3) auto-fixes stats.html CSP hash on every build.
  - Web Worker: worker-pool.js (GPL v3) added onmessageerror handler (PDF §6.1).
  - UCI: StockfishNative.java (GPL v3) tightened MultiPV/MoveOverhead/Hash/Threads
    caps + added UCI_AnalyseMode (PDF guide).
