v1.2.0 Phase 76+ (2026.7.11) — Code Smells fixes:
  - ai-bridge.js (GPL v3): _buildPGNString decomposed into 6 sub-functions
      to reduce cognitive complexity (SonarCloud CS02):
      _deriveGameResult(), _needsShredderFEN(), _formatTodayPGNDate(),
      _buildStrInfo(), _buildTimeControlTag(), _buildTerminationTag(),
      _applyShredderFENIfNeeded().
  - ai-bridge.js (GPL v3): Optional chain (?.) replaces && short-circuit
      in _needsShredderFEN() for board array access.
  - StockfishNative.java (GPL v3): Further @JavascriptInterface delegation
      to FileIoHelper (8 methods), PermissionHelper (4 methods),
      HapticHelper (hasVibrator). StockfishNative reduced from 5,443 to
      4,976 lines.

  - ui.js (GPL v3): v1.2.0 Phase 76+ further decomposition:
      _computeAndCacheVisualAnnotations (439 lines, cognitive complexity ~120)
      decomposed into 4 sub-functions:
        _replayMovesToState(moveIdx) — replays moves to get post-move state
        _computeSquareHighlights(cm, playerCol, aiCol) — Blue/Red/Yellow/Green csl
        _computeCheckArrows(cm, postState, oppKingPos, moverColor, oppColor, moveIdx)
            — Red check arrows + Green respond-to-check arrows
        _computeThreatArrows(cm, postState, moverColor, oppColor, _movedToPos, ...)
            — Yellow queen-threat arrows + Blue multi-threat arrows
      The main function now orchestrates sub-functions and caches the result.
      ui.js reduced from 8,274 to 8,115 lines.

  - ui.js (GPL v3): v1.2.0 Phase 76+ further decomposition:
      _buildEvalTrendSVG (267 lines) decomposed into 6 sub-functions:
        _getChartColors() — reads CSS variables for chart palette
        _buildEvalTrendGrid() — zero-axis line + global-mode vertical gridlines
        _buildEvalTrendSegments() — colored line segments + interpolated gap dots
        _buildEvalTrendPoints() — data point circles with fill/stroke by eval sign
        _buildEvalTrendLabels() — two-pass label rendering with overlap prevention
        _buildEvalTrendCurrentMarker() — current-position gold ring marker
      The main function now orchestrates sub-functions.
      ui.js reduced from 8,115 to 8,061 lines.
